title: Orange Earth - Race Car Passenger (2008)
description:
Recorded throughout November 2008, Race Car Passenger is the first demo to be released by Swedish alternative quartet Orange Earth.


Tracklisting:

01. To Be Found
02. Spring Night In Vienna
03. Tracing Back Our Footsteps


If you wish to support the band, feel free to spread the songs to whoever you please. Just make sure that the content of the demo remains intact and that the name of the band stays mentioned.

More about Orange Earth:
http://www.last.fm/music/Orange+Earth


Seeds are appreciated.
